title: Get Unstuck, with Super Coach Christine Hassler
description:
Master coach, author, and podcast host Christine Hassler is on the show to discuss how to start identifying the things that hold us back - from childhood issues to unhealthy patterns – in order to communicate better, set boundaries and stop people-pleasing.  

Guest Links:

Personal Mastery Program: https://christinehassler.com/mastery Use the code HEALTH (all caps) for a $200 discount for Keeping It Real listeners.
